snippet.title: Wattam E3 Trailer
snippet.description: It is our great pleasure to present the next installment in the saga of the Mayor of Wattam. Watch as they stack, chain, explode and explore a world where everyday objects spring to life! Follow us @funomena, www.funomena.com - or come meet the game's creators at E3 2015 - South Hall, IndieCade (Booth #601). We will bring fun goodies to share :D
